   The grammar has the rule
     NT31 → NT17 NT35.
   Since NT17 ⇒ “t15” at pos 1 and NT35 ⇒ “t10” at pos 2, NT31 ⇒ “t15 t10.”

3. Finally S → NT31 NT3, and NT3 ⇒ “t13” at position 3.
